Posts.Content: TammytrustsGod wrote: Hi, I had 12 of 17 nodes positive.  Just wondering how someone is doing with this stage of cancer?  I had a radical on the right and simple on the left side.  I started chemo on July 1st.  Just wanted to chat with someone who is a stage IIIC or used to be.  Or maybe someone who is triple negative to see what treatments you recieved and how you are doing.
